Riverside Resort Near Bangalore

Welcome to Area83: Your Riverside Resort Retreat Near Bangalore!

Are you tired of the hustle and bustle of city life? Yearning for a serene escape surrounded by nature's beauty?

Look no further! Area83 is your perfect getaway, nestled amidst the lush greenery near Bangalore. Whether you seek a relaxing weekend or an adventurous vacation, we have it all!

Discover the Best Riverside Resort Near Bangalore:

Area83 is proud to be one of the top riverside resorts near Bangalore. We offer a unique experience for those seeking both peace and fun.

Imagine waking up to the peaceful sound of the river, hearing the sweet songs of birds and being amazed by a stunning view.

Area83 is a great place for people who love nature and adventure. It's a perfect getaway from busy city life. Step outside your luxurious stays and nature will greet you with its soothing embrace. Our resort provides a distinctive experience featuring stunning views of the river, thrilling outdoor pursuits, and serene moments for unwinding.

At Area83, we celebrate the beauty of nature from morning to night, enjoying the misty mornings and starry nights. Experience the joy of living by the river at our resort near Bangalore. Let the magic of our place help you discover and refresh yourself.

Perfect Accommodations:

Your comfort is our priority! We offer a range of exquisite stays that cater to every need. Choose from our cozy chalet stays, luxurious suite rooms, or the ultimate experience in our private villa. We thoughtfully design each of our accommodations to provide you with the utmost relaxation and a home away from home.

Indulge in Nature's Delights:

The abundance of greenery that encompasses 90% of Area83 will thrill nature enthusiasts. Spread across a sprawling 11-acre estate, we take pride in maintaining the natural beauty of our surroundings. Stroll through our landscaped gardens, breathe in the fresh air, and immerse yourself in the lap of nature.

Spectacular Water Sports Activities:

For those seeking a splash of excitement, our 18-acre private lake offers a host of water sports activities. Embark on a thrilling kayaking adventure, glide through the waters with boating, or enjoy a leisurely ride on our water cycles. You have endless choices, and we guarantee the fun!

Floating Breakfast and More:

Start your day with a unique experience - a floating breakfast on the serene lake. Savor a sumptuous spread of delectable treats while enjoying the gentle ripples of the water beneath you. It's the perfect way to kickstart a day full of excitement and relaxation.

A Culinary Delight:

At Area83, we believe that a memorable dining experience complements a perfect getaway. Our culinary experts have curated a menu that caters to diverse palates.

Whether you crave traditional delights or international cuisine, our restaurant will delight your taste buds. Don't miss the chance for a romantic dinner at the lakeside, where the atmosphere enhances the taste of the food.

Outdoor Adventures and Relaxation:

If you seek adventure, we have you covered! Explore our resort's outdoor activities, including nature walks, trekking, and cycling trails.

Thrill-seekers can indulge in adrenaline-pumping experiences such as rock climbing and ziplining. For a more relaxed day, unwind by our pristine swimming pool, soaking in the sun and sipping on refreshing beverages.

Spa Indulgence:

A resort getaway is incomplete without rejuvenation for the mind and body. Pamper yourself at our luxurious spa resort, where skilled therapists will help you unwind with a range of treatments and therapies. Feel your worries melt away as you embrace ultimate relaxation.

Gateway to Weekend Getaways:

Area83 isn't just a destination; it's a gateway to explore nearby weekend getaways from Bangalore. Discover the beauty of the surrounding areas, each offering unique experiences and sights to behold.

Plan Your Escape:

Whether you are seeking a romantic retreat, a family vacation, or an adventure-packed weekend, Area83 has something for everyone. Create lasting memories as you immerse yourself in the tranquility of our riverside resort near Bangalore.

Book your stay now and unlock the door to paradise. Let us serve as your host and ensure your stay with us becomes a memorable experience. Come, experience Area83 - where nature embraces you, and adventure awaits!

 

Note: Area83 also offers a range of adventure packages that combine accommodations, activities, and meals to suit your preferences. Feel free to contact our team to customize your dream getaway. We can't wait to welcome you to Area83, your riverside resort near Bangalore!
